        "concepts_to_understand": "Choosing the right communication technology and method is crucial in managing communications, especially for distributed teams. Asynchronous communication allows for flexibility and ensures all team members can access and contribute to information regardless of their physical location or time zone. This supports efficient information flow in dynamic environments.",
