        "concepts_to_understand": "Effective communication involves adapting the message to the audience. When communicating with stakeholders who have different technical backgrounds, it's critical to use language and examples that resonate with them, focusing on business value and implications rather than technical minutiae. This ensures information is not just delivered but truly understood and actionable.",
